  "pn2048" : {
    "title" : "ModelTracker: Redesigning Performance Analysis Tools for Machine Learning",
    "abstract" : "Model building in machine learning is an iterative process. The performance analysis and debugging step typically involves a disruptive cognitive switch from model building to error analysis, discouraging an informed approach to model building. We present ModelTracker, an interactive visualization that subsumes information contained in numerous traditional summary statistics and graphs while displaying example-level performance and enabling direct error examination and debugging. Usage analysis from machine learning practitioners building real models with ModelTracker over six months shows ModelTracker is used often and throughout model building. A controlled experiment focusing on ModelTracker’s debugging capabilities shows participants prefer ModelTracker over traditional tools without a loss in model performance.",
    "abstract_j" : "機械学習のモデル構築 (Model building)は、反復プロセス (iterative process)である。パフォーマンス分析とデバッギング・ステップは一般的にモデル構築 (model building)からエラー (error)分析まで破壊的な認知的な切り替え (cognitive switch)を含む。そして、モデル構築 (model building)への情報に基づいたアプローチをはばむ。我々は、ModelTracker（例-レベル性能を示していて、直接のエラー (error)試験とデバッギングを可能にしている間、多数の伝統的な即時の統計学とグラフに含まれる情報を包含するインタラクティブ可視化 (visualization)）を示す。6ヵ月の間ModelTrackerで本当のモデルを造っている機械学習実務家 (practitioners)からの使用分析法は、ModelTrackerがしばしば使われて、モデル構築 (model building)を通してあることを示す。ModelTrackerのデバッギング能力に集中している統制実験 (controlled experiment)は、参加者 (participants)が典型的な公演で損失なしで伝統的なツール (tools)の上にModelTrackerを好むことを示す。",
    "abstract_c" : "模型建筑 (building)在机器学习是一个迭代过程 (process)。该表现 (performance)分析和调试步骤 (step)通常涉及从模型建筑 (building)到错误 (error)分析，一个颠覆性的认知开关 (switch)劝阻知情途径 (approach)模型建筑 (building)。我们提出ModelTracker，互动可视化 (visualization)是涵括信息 (information)同时显示例如级表现 (performance)，使直接错误 (error)检查和调试包含众多传统总结 (summary)统计数据和图表。从学习机使用情况分析实践者 (practitioners)建立真正的模型 (models)与ModelTracker半年以上显示ModelTracker往往和整个模型建筑 (building)使用。受控实验 (experiment)重点ModelTracker的调试功能显示被试；参与者 (participants)喜欢ModelTracker比传统工具 (tools)没有模型表现 (performance)亏损。",
    "abstract_k" : "기계 학습의 모델 만들기 (building)는 반복 절차 (process)입니다. 성능 (performance) 분석 및 디버깅 단계 (step)는 일반적으로 만들기 (building)을 모델링 정보 접근법 (approach)을 깎아 오류 (error) 분석에 모델 만들기 (building)에서 파괴인지 스위치 (switch)을 포함한다. 우리는 ModelTracker, 예를 들어 레벨 성능 (performance)를 표시하고 직접 오류 (error) 검사 및 디버깅을 가능하게하고있는 동안 많은 전통적인 개요 (summary) 통계 및 그래프에 포함 정보 (information)을 포섭 대화 형 시각화 (visualization)을 제시한다. 기계 학습에서 사용 현황 분석은 ModelTracker 자주와 모델 만들기 (building) 전반에 걸쳐 사용되는 6 개월 동안 ModelTracker과 실제 모델 (models)을 보여줍니다 구축 실무자 (practitioners) . ModelTracker의 디버깅 기능에 초점을 맞추고 제어 실험 (experiment)는 참가자 (participants) 모델 성능 (performance)의 손실없이 기존의 도구 (tools)을 통해 ModelTracker을 선호 보여줍니다.",
    "cAndB" : "Presents ModelTracker, an interactive visualization of machine learning models. Field and controlled studies show that ModelTracker encourages more informed model building by enabling frequent and direct data inspection and debugging.",
    "keywords" : [ "Machine Learning", "Interactive Visualization", "Performance Analysis", "Debugging." ],
