  "pn2272" : {
    "title" : "The Smartphone Project - An Augmented Dance Performance",
    "abstract" : "The Smartphone Project (TSP) is an interactive dance-performance in a professional setting that exploits the communication channels provided by smartphone-apps as a new material in the dance-theatre domain. We present an account of the experience and its staging. Based on an initial study with 36 participants from the audience, we present results and discuss lessons learned from this project that might guide similar future work. ",
    "abstract_j" : "スマートフォン (Smartphone) Project（TSP）は、ダンス劇場領域の新しい材料として多機能電話-アプリにより提供されるコミュニケーション (communication)チャンネルを利用する専門のセッティングの双方向ダンス公演である。我々は、経験とその足がかりの報告を発表する。観衆から36の参加者 (participants)で最初の研究に基づいて、我々は結果を提示して、類似した将来の仕事を導くかもしれないこのプロジェクトから、得られた知見 (lessons learned)を協議する。",
    "abstract_c" : "该智能手机 (Smartphone) 项目 (Project)（TSP）是一个互动的舞蹈表现，它利用作为舞蹈剧场领域 (domain)新材料所提供的智能手机应用程序的沟通 (communication)频道的专业设置。我们目前的经验 (experience)及其分期的账户 (account)。根据初始研究 (study) 36 被试；参与者 (participants)观众，我们提出结果 (results)从这个项目 (project)可能类似指导今后的工作讨论学到的教训 (lessons learned)。",
    "abstract_k" : "스마트폰 (Smartphone) 프로젝트 (Project) (TSP)는 댄스 극장 도메인 (domain)의 새로운 재료로 스마트 폰 앱에서 제공하는 의사소통 (communication) 채널을 악용하는 전문 상황 (setting)에서 상호 작용하는 댄스 퍼포먼스이다. 우리는 경험 (experience)과 준비의 계정 (account)을 제시한다. 관객 36 참가자 (participants)와 초기 연구 (study)을 바탕으로, 우리는 결과 (results)을 제시하고 유사한 미래의 작업을 안내 할 수이 프로젝트 (project)에서 교훈 (lessons learned)에 대해 설명합니다.",
    "cAndB" : "The Smartphone Project is a novel interactive dance-performance in a professional theatre setting that explores the smartphone as a material and an artistic medium. It premiered at the Pina40 festival.",
    "keywords" : [ "Audience interaction", "dance", "theatre", "augmented reality", "smartphone", "material", "mixed reality", "art", "performance" ],
